title: About
text: This is a blog space for Austin ML Journal Club. We are a small group of ML practitioners based in Austin, TX. We are a diverse group with various backgrounds and interests. We are interested in learning state-of-the-art ML techniques and best practices from papers and also from each other. We kicked off our first meeting in Oct, 2022.
